# Test files and migrations
# Most research_harness tests + the v0_citrag_05 fixture are local-dev only
# (they read backend/data/ or need a live LLM). The CI-safe subset below is
# force-tracked: pure-logic, network-free, no fixture dependency. The one
# fixture-backed case in test_research_harness_citation.py auto-skips when the
# fixture is absent. See docs/research-harness-roadmap.md (Step 4 decision).
backend/tests/*
!backend/tests/test_research_harness_prompts.py
!backend/tests/test_research_harness_citation.py
!backend/tests/test_research_harness_honest_gate.py
backend/migrations/

